In article <15311@ucbvax.BERKELEY.EDU> desj@brahms.UUCP (David desJardins) wri
tes:
>I give up -- what does an "orb of dragon slaying" do for me?  I went all
>the way through the game without ever seeing one -- now I find it on level 1!

>What is it?
>
>   -- David desJardins


The orb of dragon slaying is one of the four special items in larn.
List as following:
           Item.            Char.                  Rem.
  -------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Theft prevent device.      (.)         Stop the Leppies and Nymies
                                         stealing your stuff.
  Undead control             (@)         Stop the Vamp. and Wraith
                                         attacking you.
  Scarab of negate spirit.   (:)         Same as undead control except
                                         this work on the n & x.
  Orb of dragon slaying.     (o)         Killing dragons efficiently.
  --------------------------------------------------------------------------

